{"tid":2335864,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕節買玩具黃店推介 - 深水埗篇","createTime":"2020-12-22T07:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T10:36:10.000Z","uid":13361,"like":73,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a96e32b08ed493f1a3925e908e884fc4c33623","tid":2335864,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"送比男朋友系列 - 福利模型 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多高達 小妹就買咗隻渣古比男朋友 因為男朋友話渣古係男人嘅浪漫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6agUYy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6agUYy.jpg&h=d3dfb81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />男朋友收到一定好開心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本土lego系列  - 玩具帝國<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwL43SF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwL43SF.jpg&h=3f014894&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LA2yXcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLA2yXcG.jpg&h=cfe1eeee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUKNhcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUKNhcG.jpg&h=3b75dcce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6gLOjn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6gLOjn.jpg&h=33ac1d72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeDioSH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeDioSH.jpg&h=c154cead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多好特別嘅lego 用黎聖誕抽獎岩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有爆旋陀螺買夠唔同價錢有折 <br />\n<br />\n送比小朋友系列 - 甲蟲部屋 &amp; 關東店Kanto hobby <br />\n<br />\n甲蟲部屋 黃過爛屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYzJz0V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYzJz0V.png&h=e9a5a38a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEW71Ga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEW71Ga.png&h=3f79d4a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4MjSN2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4MjSN2.png&h=62620af0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4AwJUP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4AwJUP.png&h=b4a253c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKanto hobby<br />\n<br />\n門口賣啲$20 $10 玩具 勁多c9搶住買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意返 夜晚去可能多人到仆街 除咗玩具帝國平時都無咩人 福利平時成日都要排隊入去<br />\n另外兩間仲要係正玩具街入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585b37bf2e2e4e62fa947edade3ff6313580bc8b","tid":2335864,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"華富邨幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace524e3ed41a743157e96d8bf5e2bfa99a1e247","tid":2335864,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29012a9ebaeeb6a15dace07b889641d34d1c72c7","tid":2335864,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"585b37bf2e2e4e62fa947edade3ff6313580bc8b","tid":2335864,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:48:20.000Z","msg":"華富邨幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:50:09.000Z","msg":"一陣幫你望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8759db1a34a892e36542f8e0c34241a9ec3c1671","tid":2335864,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29012a9ebaeeb6a15dace07b889641d34d1c72c7","tid":2335864,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"585b37bf2e2e4e62fa947edade3ff6313580bc8b","tid":2335864,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTi